# 🛍️ E-Commerce Data Platform

A modern, serverless data engineering platform for e-commerce analytics built on AWS. Generates realistic synthetic data, ingests it into a data lake, catalogs with Glue, and visualizes with Streamlit.

**Status**: ✅ Production Ready

---

## 📊 Features

- **Data Ingestion** - Lambda-based synthetic data generator
- **Data Lake** - S3-based medallion architecture (Bronze layer)
- **Data Catalog** - AWS Glue automatic schema discovery
- **Querying** - Athena SQL queries on data lake
- **Analytics** - Interactive Streamlit dashboard
- **Monitoring** - DynamoDB watermarks + SNS alerts
- **IaC** - CloudFormation for infrastructure as code

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```
Data Sources (Lambda)
    ↓
S3 Bronze Layer (Raw Data)
    ↓
AWS Glue Crawler (Catalog)
    ↓
Glue Data Catalog (Schema)
    ↓
Athena (SQL Queries)
    ↓
Streamlit Dashboard (Visualization)
```

### Components

| Component | Purpose | Technology |
|---|---|---|
| **Data Generation** | Create realistic e-commerce data | AWS Lambda + Python |
| **Storage** | Raw data storage | Amazon S3 |
| **Catalog** | Schema discovery & metadata | AWS Glue |
| **Metadata** | Pipeline state tracking | DynamoDB |
| **Querying** | SQL on data lake | Amazon Athena |
| **Alerts** | Pipeline notifications | SNS |
| **Dashboard** | Interactive analytics | Streamlit + Plotly |
| **Infrastructure** | Resource provisioning | CloudFormation |

---

## 📦 What Gets Generated

### Products (50 records)
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Electronics Product 1",
  "price": 299.99,
  "category": "ELECTRONICS",
  "rating": {"rate": 4.5, "count": 127}
}
```

### Customers (100 records)
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "email": "john.smith1@email.com",
  "name": {"firstname": "John", "lastname": "Smith"},
  "address": {
    "city": "New York",
    "street": "5234 Main St",
    "zipcode": "45678"
  }
}
```

### Orders (200 records)
```json
{
  "id": 1,
  "userId": 42,
  "date": "2026-05-15",
  "products": [{"productId": 7, "quantity": 2}],
  "status": "completed"
}
```

### Events (500 records)
```json
{
  "event_id": "uuid-123",
  "event_type": "page_view",
  "timestamp": "2026-06-02T12:34:56",
  "user_id": 15,
  "device": "desktop"
}
```

