| Service | Monthly Limit | Cost |
|---|---|---|
| **Lambda** | 1M invocations | FREE |
| **S3** | 5 GB | FREE |
| **DynamoDB** | 25 GB on-demand | FREE |
| **Glue** | 1M objects | FREE |
| **Athena** | 1 TB scanned | ~$5 |
| **CloudFormation** | Unlimited | FREE |
| **SNS** | 1000 emails | FREE |
| **Total** | | **~$5/month** |

