## 📁 Project Structure

```
ecommerce-data-platform/
├── cloudformation/
│   └── template.yaml              # Infrastructure definition
├── lambda/
│   ├── data-generator/
│   │   └── index.py               # Data generation logic (350+ lines)
│   └── data-quality/
│       └── index.py               # Quality checks
├── spark/
│   └── jobs/
│       ├── bronze_to_silver.py     # Data transformation (future)
│       └── silver_to_gold.py       # Aggregations (future)
├── scripts/
│   ├── deploy.ps1                 # PowerShell deployment
│   ├── deploy.sh                  # Bash deployment
│   └── cleanup.sh                 # Resource cleanup
├── dashboard.py                   # Streamlit app
├── README.md                      # This file
├── GETTING_STARTED.md             # Quick guide
├── requirements.txt               # Python dependencies
└── docs/
    └── ARCHITECTURE.md            # Detailed architecture
```

