## 🔧 Configuration

### Environment Variables

Lambda functions use:
- `DATA_LAKE_BUCKET` - S3 bucket name
- `WATERMARK_TABLE` - DynamoDB watermarks table

### CloudFormation Parameters

- `ProjectName` (default: `ecommerce-data-platform`) - Used for all resource naming

