## 🛠️ Maintenance

### Clean Up Resources

**Delete everything (careful!):**
```powershell
aws s3 rb s3://ecommerce-data-platform-datalake-211854352436 --force

aws cloudformation delete-stack --stack-name ecommerce-data-platform-stack-v2 --region us-east-1
```

### View Logs

**Lambda logs:**
```powershell
aws logs tail /aws/lambda/ecommerce-data-platform-data-generator --follow
```

**Glue Crawler logs:**
```powershell
aws glue get-crawler-metrics --crawler-name ecommerce-data-platform-bronze-crawler
```

---

## 🚨 Troubleshooting

### Issue: Lambda execution fails
**Solution**: Check CloudWatch logs
```powershell
aws logs tail /aws/lambda/ecommerce-data-platform-data-generator --follow
```

### Issue: Glue Crawler doesn't find tables
**Solution**: Manually run crawler and wait 2-3 minutes
```powershell
aws glue start-crawler --name ecommerce-data-platform-bronze-crawler --region us-east-1
```

### Issue: Streamlit can't connect to S3
**Solution**: Ensure AWS credentials are configured
```powershell
aws configure
```

### Issue: CloudFormation stack creation fails
**Solution**: Check Events tab in CloudFormation console

